imdb.plot outline: A travel and adventure series taking you through some of the most extreme regions on Earth, from the Amazonian jungle to Alaska's icebergs, from Africa to Tibet, from Sahara to the top of Mount Everest. It's not just about the places, but about people, culture, history and life.
